name: Uthil_Ren%27kacal
content: Uthil Ren'kacal was a Gotal male bounty hunter active during the Galactic Civil War. He was part of the team led by Zinn Classet, Ren'kacal assisted in the hunt for Alliance to Restore the Republic operatives who had angered the Spice Mines of Kessel by freeing a Wookiee slave, Kentara. He wore a full length blue coat, and was adorned with jewelry. A large scar on Ren'kacal's left cheek was decorated with earrings. Ren'kacal worked as the group's tracker, and was not very skilled in a fight.
